divs: sighting details i was walking through montauk with my family when my mom noticed the object. i looked at it and at first thought they were two ballons. after watching it i noticed they were stationary an about 3\4 to a mile away. i took a picture and thought nothing of it. about 15 minutes later i looked back and they had not moved! when i returned home i looked closely at the photo. it appears to have a source of light in the center of each object. they do not appear to be connected either. the reason i took this long to report it is because i had just found out about m.u.f.o.n. a few days ago. note: these objects were sighted in montauk near camp hero. camp hero is a state park and visitors are welcome. camp hero is believed to be retired but 75% is still off limit. also, the government owns 4 levels under the surface and the state just the surface.
